{
  "stem": "26609.11",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was how it was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Until the ghetto was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they took them out?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What they did there, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Cleaned, I think-- cleaned them and scrubbed and whatever they did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the German-- how do you call it-- was a [GERMAN] or whatever, there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They stood there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were a few thousand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Park Stryiskyi.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I gave it to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You have it written down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It came back to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It comes back if I-- When I talk, I don't think of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when I think deeper, it comes back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Stryiskyi Park, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They called it park.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was more a huge one-- a big one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But what they did there, I think-- women sewing their military clothing-- sewing, cleaning, that was-- or maybe for their kitchen, they cook-- they peeled potatoes, or they prepared for-- they had a big kitchen for the army, there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's what they did there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't go-- I was not in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came back from the hospital, there, because I had nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot about this in my pocket, that I had the paper of that-- address of that Polish woman who helped my sister-- younger sister.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But from the hospital I went back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think that I stayed only one night there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And next day, when I discovered the paper that I had-- that woman-- and because I didn't have the child-- she didn't want to take me with the child.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I told you before how I came into her place-- to the Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She went out from the ghetto, the eldest sister, with her husband, when they went to work in the morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was before the ghetto was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
